OL,3,CCountry park loses over 100 trees to
OL,4,Cstorm as pictures show scale of damage
OL,6,FA country park in Bannau Brycheiniog
OL,7,FNational Park has been forced to close
OL,8,Fafter Storm Darragh brought down more
OL,9,Fthan 100 trees.
OL,11,FCraig-y-nos Country Park is
OL,12,Ftemporarily closed after the storm
OL,13,Fbrought down more than 100 trees,
OL,14,Fsignificantly altering the landscape
OL,15,Fof the site, which is a 40-acre
OL,16,FVictorian garden managed by the
OL,17,Fnational park.
