OL,6,FStorm Darragh saw a rare red weather
OL,7,Fwarning put in place for large parts
OL,8,Fof Wales on Saturday, 7 December,
OL,9,Fleading to homes being damaged, power
OL,10,Foutages and wide-scale travel
OL,11,Fdisruption.
OL,13,FIn a statement, a Bannau Brycheiniog
OL,14,FNational Park spokesperson said: "The
OL,15,Fpark will remain closed this week and
OL,16,Fpossibly longer to allow teams to
OL,17,Fsafely assess the damage and carry out
OL,18,Fessential clearance and repair work.
