OL,3,CCountry park loses over 100 trees to
OL,4,Cstorm as pictures show scale of damage
OL,6,F"Our priority is visitor safety. Due
OL,7,Fto the scale of the damage, we require
OL,8,Fspecialist contractors to clear the
OL,9,Farea. These contractors are currently
OL,10,Fin high demand following the
OL,11,Fwidespread impact of the storm.
OL,13,F"The closure is part of a broader
OL,14,Fresponse across the Bannau Brycheiniog
OL,15,FNational Park, as warden teams work to
OL,16,Fevaluate and repair damage from Storm
OL,17,FDarragh.
